title: Green Jello live at the Kennel Club San Francisco 4-10-91.mp3
description:
Green Jello recorded live at the Kennel Club in San Francisco April 10, 1991. Ran this tape through 2 sequential equalizers years ago, as best I remember, to improve to improve the sound quality. Was a fun show and captures them at their best and before they changed their name to Green Jelly. 

PLEASE PLEASE SEED WHEN DONE. IF YOU DO THEN I CAN SHARE MORE STUFF.
